12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. There is hereby appropriated to the Oklahoma Water
14 Resources Board from any monies not otherwise appropriated from the
15 Progressing Rural Economic Prosperity Fund of the State Treasury
16 created in Section 256 of Title 62 of the Oklahoma Statutes, the sum
17 of Two Million Dollars ($2,000,000.00) for the purpose of providing
18 water infrastructure funding to a rural water sewer and solid waste
19 management district in the central region of the state experiencing
20 private water well contamination from an unknown source and needing
21 connected with a public water supply.
22 SECTION 2. There is hereby appropriated to the Oklahoma Water
23 Resources Board from any monies not otherwise appropriated from the
24 Progressing Rural Economic Prosperity Fund of the State Treasury
